PropertyClassDef.Name: BooleanQuery
PropertyClassDef.Description: Used to allow True/False inlines to be associated with column for query forms

Property.Name: ZwmDerQtyPickedInPPS
Property.Expression: ISNULL((SELECT TOP 1 SUM(ISNULL(picklistref.qty_picked,0)) FROM pick_list_ref picklistref JOIN pick_list picklist ON picklist.pick_list_id = picklistref.pick_list_id WHERE picklistref.ref_line_suf = TrnLine AND picklistref.ref_num = TrnNum AND picklist.status = 'P'),0)

Property.Name: ZwmDerQtyToPickInPPS
Property.Expression: ISNULL((SELECT TOP 1 SUM(ISNULL(picklistref.qty_to_pick,0)) FROM pick_list_ref picklistref JOIN pick_list picklist ON picklist.pick_list_id = picklistref.pick_list_id WHERE picklistref.ref_line_suf = TrnLine AND picklistref.ref_num = TrnNum AND picklist.status = 'O'),0)

Property.Name: ZwmDerQtyToShipInPPS
Property.Expression: ISNULL((SELECT TOP 1 SUM(ISNULL(shipseq.qty_picked,0)) FROM shipment_seq shipseq JOIN shipment_line shipline ON shipline.shipment_id = shipseq.shipment_id AND shipline.shipment_line = shipseq.shipment_line JOIN pick_list_ref picklistref ON picklistref.pick_list_id = shipline.pick_list_id AND picklistref.sequence = shipline.pick_list_ref_sequence JOIN coitem coitem ON coitem.co_num = picklistref.ref_num AND coitem.co_line = picklistref.ref_line_suf AND coitem.co_release = picklistref.ref_release AND picklistref.ref_type = 'O' JOIN shipment ship ON ship.shipment_id = shipseq.shipment_id AND ship.status <> 'S' WHERE coitem.co_line = TrnLine AND coitem.co_num = TrnNum),0)
